### Listar todas las órdenes
GET {{host}}/api/v1/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Obtener una orden por ID
GET {{host}}/api/v1/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Crear una nueva orden
POST {{host}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "customerId": "ALFKI",
  "employeeId": 1,
  "orderDate": "2024-04-08",
  "requiredDate": "2024-04-15",
  "shipperId": 1,
  "freight": 32.50,
  "shipName": "Alfred's Futterkiste",
  "shipAddress": "Obere Str. 57",
  "shipCity": "Berlin",
  "shipCountry": "Germany",
  "details": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "unitPrice": 18.00,
      "quantity": 5,
      "discount": 0.0
    }
  ]
}

### Actualización Parcial de una orden (PATCH)
# Ejemplo: cambiando solo el transportista (shipperId)
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/orders/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "shipperId": 2
}

### Marcar orden como enviada (Ship)
# Esto asignará automáticamente la fecha de envío actual
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/orders/1/ship
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Cancelar una orden
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/orders/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Eliminar una orden (Deprecated)
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
